Description:
    Create or update ManageIQ provider plugin

Example:
    rails generate manageiq:ph_infra_provider ManageIQ::Providers::VendorName
    rails generate manageiq:ph_infra_provider ManageIQ::Providers::VendorName --path ~/dev
    rails generate manageiq:ph_infra_provider ManageIQ::Providers::VendorName --vcr --dummy --dev --ui
